{"word":"ἀντήλιος","slug":"ἀντήλιος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n9762\" key=\"a)nth/lios\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἀντήλιος</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ἀντί, ἥλιος</etym>) <sense id=\"n9762.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">opposite the sun,</tr_> i.e. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">looking east,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg003.perseus-grc1:805\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Aj.\">Aj.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">805</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg010.perseus-grc1:1550\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ion\">Ion</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1550</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">δαίμονες ἀντήλιοι</foreign> statues of gods <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">which stood in the sun</tr_> before the house-door, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg005.perseus-grc1:519\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ag.\">Ag.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">519</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"Eur. Fr. 538\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Fr.\">Fr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">538</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n9762.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of the moon, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">reflecting the sun's rays,</tr_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ AB\">AB</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">403</biblScope> </bibl> (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ἀνθ-</etym>), cf. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Suid.</author> </bibl>: hence metaph., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">imitation, reflection,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0566.tlg001:367\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Theopomp.Hist.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">367</biblScope> </bibl> (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ἀνθ-</etym>). </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n9762.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀντήλια, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τά</gen>,</foreign> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">παρήλια</ref></xr>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">parhelia,</tr_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Suid.</author></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0541.tlg001:511\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Men.\">Men.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">511</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n9762.3\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">screens</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">parasols,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4083.tlg001:1281:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eust.\">Eust.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1281.3</biblScope> </bibl>; also, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">blinkers</tr_> on horses' bridles, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0542.tlg001:10:54\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Poll.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.54</biblScope> </bibl> (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ἀνθ-</etym>), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4083.tlg001:1562:39\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eust.\">Eust.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1562.39</biblScope></bibl>.—The <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ion.\">Ion.</a></gram> </gramGrp> form <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀντήλιος</foreign> is always used in Trag.; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀνθήλιος</foreign> first in Theopomp. l.c., cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0018.tlg001:1:656\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ph.\">Ph.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.656</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Placit.\">Placit.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.6</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}